		<title>在ドイツの米核兵器維持に、過半数が賛成</title>
		<link>https://midori1kwh.de/2022/06/20/13359?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=%25e5%259c%25a8%25e3%2583%2589%25e3%2582%25a4%25e3%2583%2584%25e3%2581%25ae%25e7%25b1%25b3%25e6%25a0%25b8%25e5%2585%25b5%25e5%2599%25a8%25e7%25b6%25ad%25e6%258c%2581%25e3%2581%25ab%25e3%2580%2581%25e9%2581%258e%25e5%258d%258a%25e6%2595%25b0%25e3%2581%258c%25e8%25b3%259b%25e6%2588%2590</link>
